<plot>THUNDER AT A PLAYHOUSE follows several very different teenagers as they negotiate the challenges of putting on a Shakespeare play in three weeks. Facing challenges ranging from line-learning to romantic entanglements, these young people learn invaluable lessons about themselves while also rediscovering the language they grew up with.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?606666</url></doc>
